What people say about Regroover





Regroover is an amazing plugin. Pretty crazy! I will definitely be using this on records. Instantly! 

Mischke (Songwriter/Producer) - Michael Jackson, Trey Songz, Pussycat Dolls, Jessica Simpson, Jennifer Lopez, Spice Girls, KC & JoJo 



 
 
 
 
 

 
 







