SPECIFICATIONS



MAC OSX



      
Versions 10.8.5 or later (64-bit)
AU (32/64-bit), VST (32/64-bit) and AAX (64-bit)
RAM: 2GB (4+ GB recommended)
Monitor: 1280-by-800 resolution or higher
Hard Disk space: 250MB
        




WINDOWS



      
Versions 7 SP1 or later
VST (32/64-bit) and AAX (64-bit)
 RAM: 2GB (4+ GB recommended)
 Monitor: 1280-by-800 resolution or higher
 Hard Disk space: 250MB
        






DAW COMPATIBILITY



TESTED



      
We have tested Regroover in the following DAWs: Ableton Live 9.5, Logic Pro 10.2, Steinberg Cubase 7.5 (64-bit only), Avid Pro Tools 11.3 and 12.5, Cockos Reaper 5.22, Presonus Studio One 3.0, , Bitwig Studio 2.0, ImageLine FL Studio 12.0. If you don’t see your DAW here, you can always download the free, fully-functional 14-day trial and see if your DAW is supported. If you encounter any problems, let us know and we'll do our best to support your setup.
        




UNSUPPORTED



      
We don't currently support the following DAWs: Steinberg Cubase 32-bit
        







